<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>SF Hacks Check-in Link</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <div
      style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;"
    >
      <h1 style="color: #5a67d8;">Your SF Hacks Check-In Link</h1>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">Hi there,</p>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
        We would like to remind you that you are accepted for SF Hacks 2025. Screenshot this code and show it to us at the door. 
      </p>

      <a
        href="{{qrCodeLink}}"
        style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; background-color: #5a67d8; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;"
      >
        View Check-In Code
      </a>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 20px;">
        Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
      </p>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #5a67d8; word-break: break-all;">
        <a href="{{qrCodeLink}}" style="color: #5a67d8;">{{qrCodeLink}}</a>
      </p>

      <hr style="margin: 30px 0;" />

      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #333;">
        If you’re no longer able to attend, please take a moment to let us know by filling out this quick form:
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://tally.so/r/wdz4Qd"
        style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 12px; background-color: #e53e3e; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;"
        target="_blank"
      >
        I’m No Longer Attending
      </a>

      <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 30px; color: #777;">See you soon at SF Hacks!</p>

      <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 13px; color: #999999;">
        SF Hacks | San Francisco State University |
        <a href="https://sfhacks.io" style="color: #5a67d8;">sfhacks.io</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
